  {
    "direction": null,
    "content": "<p>In a given 8-bit general purpose micro-controller there are following flags.</p>\n<p>C-Carry, A-Auxiliary Carry, O-Overflow flag, P-Parity (0 for even, 1 for odd)</p>\n<p>R$$_0$$ and R$$_1$$ are the two general purpose registers of the micro-controller.</p>\n<p>After execution of the following instructions, the decimal equivalent of the binary sequence of the flag pattern [CAOP] will be _________.</p>\n<p>MOV R0, +0x60</p>\n<p>MOV R1, +0x46</p>\n<p>ADD R0, R1</p>",
    "options": [],
    "correct_options": [],
    "answer": "2",
    "explanation": "<p>$$ \\begin{aligned} & \\mathrm{R} 0 \\leftarrow 60 \\mathrm{H} \\\\ & \\mathrm{R} 1 \\leftarrow 46 \\mathrm{H} \\end{aligned} $$</p>\n\n<p>ADDR0,R1 $\\Rightarrow$</p>\n\n<p>$\\begin{array}{r}01100000 \\\\ +01000110 \\\\ \\hline 1010 \\quad 0110 \\\\ \\hline\\end{array}$</p>\n\n<p>$\\therefore$ Carry flag $=0$</p>\n\n<p>Over flow flag $=1$</p>\n\n<p>Auxiliary carry flag $=0$</p>\n\n<p>Parity flag $=0$</p>\n\n<p>$\\mathrm{CAOP}=(0010)_2=(2)_{10}$</p>",
    "topic": null,
    "year": 2023,
    "yearKey": "gate-ee-2023",
    "difficulty": null
  },
